@DATABASE "Motorbike Madness"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Motorbike Madness"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                             Motorbike Madness
                             =================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33321,255)"}          33321,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33551,195)"}          33551,195

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I haven't tested this one as I don't have the
                         game :(

                         Rastan
@endnode
